          "explanation": "Given image is showing absent bronchioalveolar markings of right lung with tracheal shift towards left side which is suggestive of right pneumothorax. Pneumothorax: presence of air or gas in pleural cavity Also remember, Deep sulcus sign on supine chest X-ray in expiration phase is a feature of pneumothorax.",
