          "correctOptionId": "opt-1",
          "explanation": "Isoflurane more than other inhalational agents increases coronary blood flow many times beyond that of the myocardial oxygen demand, thereby, creating potential for \"Steel\", steel is diversion of blood from a myocardial bed with limited or inadequate perfusion to a bed with more adequate perfusion.",
