          "explanation": "LMA is intermediate between the face mask and Endotracheal intubation in terms of reliability, invasiveness and facilitation of gas exchance (face mask has minimum and endotracheal intubation has maximum).\nLMA does not prevent aspiration -4 should not be used in full stomach patients.\nLMA can be used as an alternative to endotracheal intubation for minor surgeries, where anaesthetist wants to avoid intubation.\nLMA is introduced blindly (without laryngoscopy)."
