          "id": "medmcqa-6a0341cd-0fbb-4039-bbbf-0977c51365e4",
          "text": "Following A, a patient suffered splenic ruture. His BP is 90/60 mmHg, PR 126/min and Sp02 92%. Induction agent of choice is",
