          "id": "medmcqa-d5ec4923-de6a-4951-869c-a3edcfe30773",
          "text": "A 30-year-old woman in her last trimester of pregnancy suddenly develops massive swelling of the left lower extremity. Which of the following would be the most appropriate workup and treatment at this time",
