          "id": "medmcqa-94b46209-d203-4b3e-9100-27ffa848b44a",
          "text": "19-year-old boy was posted for emergency repair of the ruptured globe .The patient had last meal 5 hr ago. Which among the following is anesthetic technique of choice in this patient ?",
