          "explanation": "There are two sources of gases (O2, N2O & air) for anaesthetic machine :-\n\n\nCylinder          → High pressure system\nPipeline source → Intermediate pressure system\n\n\nOxygen flush delivers 35-75 liters of oxygen per minute."
