          "explanation": "According, the rate of systemic absorption is greatest with intercostal nerve blocks followed by caudal, lumbar epidural, brachial plexus block femoral and sciatic nerve blocks. Sequence of systemic absorption IV > Tracheal > Intercostal block > Para cervical block > Caudal > Lumbar epidural > Brachial Plexus > Sciatic > Subcutaneous.",
