          "correctOptionId": "opt-3",
          "explanation": "Sch is the only muscle relaxant that causes vagal stimulation and causes bradycardia (attenuates tachycardia and hypeension ) In burns, crush injury and myasthenia gravis can cause severe hyperkalemia. Ref: Morgan 4th/e p 214",
          "hint": "Topic: Muscle relaxants"
