          "correctOptionId": "opt-2",
          "explanation": "Desflurane has lowest blood : gas solubility and moreover its fat solubility is also very less. thus recovery very fast even in obese Thus Desflurane requires less downward titration in surgical procedures to achieve a rapid emergence by viue of decreased tissue saturation. This may be paicularly advantages in the morbidly obese patient.",
