          "correctOptionId": "opt-2",
          "explanation": "Benzodiazepines are drugs that exe in slightly varying degrees, five principles pharmacologic effects: 1. Anxiolysis 2. Sedation 3. Anticonvulsant actions 4. Skeletal muscle relaxation 5. Anterograde amnesia",
