          "correctOptionId": "opt-1",
          "explanation": "Mobitz type 2 heart block is an active cardiac condition that needs further evaluation before proceeding to surgery.\nDyspnea at rest or with minimal exertion, decompensated cardiac failure, severe stenotic valvular lesions are other conditions."
